#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Permissions at higher levels are Field Level permissions. All Fields have a "
"Permission Level set against them and the rules defined at that permissions "
"apply to the field. This is useful in case you want to hide or make certain "
"field read-only for certain Roles."
